<p style="Heading 2" xid="284" props="text-indent:0in; margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in"><c props="font-weight:bold">How this book is organized</c></p>
<p style="Standard" xid="285" props="font-size:11pt">This book has 4 main sections called -</p>
<p style="Standard" xid="286" props="font-size:11pt"><c></c></p>
